snippet.title: Genfanad - Old School MMORPG - Tutorial Quest Area
snippet.description:
In this video you can get a quick look into Genfanad's tutorial quest area where a player learns the basics of the game before entering the open world where adventure will await for him.


The game is still under development.


Discord - https://bit.ly/3ktq9W3


(This game is not Runescape Classic, it is not owned by anyway by Jagex or their employees, it does not use any assets/graphics/lore of Jagex. It is however inspired by Runescape Classic)
